channel.title: Anyone have any idea why my woodcutting doesn't work?
channel.description:
I have all the code necessary. The same code frugoo and funescap3 uses for woodcutting. Except, I can't woodcut! If you select chop (xtree) it does nothing. And yes don't ask "lol did you have an axe equipped" because I did.
Anything special you have to do outside the client? Or is there anything in the client.java that isn't labeld ~HELLO WOODCUTTING~ maybe some kind of hidden command? I don't know just something that will make my woodcutting work please?!
